Yes, in beginExtractReceiptFromUrl was about adding convenience to the users. But adding overloads for beginExtractReceipt would only take away the pollInterval and includeTextDetails  and would be overly simplifying things for the user.
Not sure, if we would want that.
@srnagar @JonathanGiles Thoughts?

